spec_data.Name: python-django-socialregistration
spec_data.Description:
Django Social Registration enables developers to add alternative registration
methods based on third party sites.

Supported methods currently are:

    OpenID
    OAuth
    Instagram

spec_data.Summary: Django application enabling registration through a variety of APIs
